description:
1️⃣ A sword that feels uncomfortably weighty towards the
blade. Still swingable, and would still cut shit.
name: Imbalanced Sword

description:
2️⃣ Impeccably normal and regularly-forged iron sword.
Is kinda heavy, though.
name: Iron Sword

description:
3️⃣⭐ An unusually glowy blade for a "sword in the stone" type of weapon.
Imbued with "Energy", may purge causing \State[1](2%) on-hit.
name: "Light Thrust"

description:
4️⃣ When forging swords with Noire, apparently they become rather sinister-looking.
Imbued with "Void", may slay causing \State[1](1%) on-hit.
name: Dark Slash

description:
6️⃣ Further upgrading the quality of Noire is starting to make the blade look like midnight.
Imbued with "Void", may slay causing \State[1](2%) on-hit.
name: Nocturnal Blade

description:
7️⃣⭐ The glow of the blade appears to have sharpened the blade to a fine point.
Imbued with "Energy", may purge causing \State[1](4%) on-hit.
name: "Sacred Spine"

description:
9️⃣ At the peak of galactic design, we have this- the Dimension Blade, renderer of the heavens.
Imbued with "Void", may slay causing \State[1](3%) on-hit.
name: Dimension Blade

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended blade of pure energy, renowned for cleaving foes in twain.
Imbued with "Energy", may purge causing \State[1](6%) on-hit.
name: "Claidheamh Soluis"

description:
2️⃣ A massive blade that simply cannot be wielded in one-hand.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Two-Handed Sword

description:
4️⃣ Forged with a nice chunk of verte, this sizeable chopper was born.
Imbued with "Air", may apply \State[11](25%) on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: Wind Cleaver

description:
5️⃣⭐ Are you trying to compensate by wielding this monstrously large chunk of rock?
Imbued with "Ground", may apply \State[12](25%) on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: "Colossus"

description:
6️⃣ Empowered with the blessing of the mountain winds, you still aren't very fast while holding this.
Imbued with "Air", may apply \State[11](50%) on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: Cyclone Sword

description:
8️⃣⭐⭐ A colossal weapon reinforced with the finest ores.
Imbued with "Ground", may apply \State[12](50%) on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: "Juggernaut"

description:
6️⃣ Empowered with the blessing of the mountain winds, you still aren't very fast while holding this.
Imbued with "Air", applies \State[11] on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: Storm Cleaver

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended blade of dragon-slaying might, able to take down any reptile around!
Imbued with "Ground", applies \State[12] on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: "Lævateinn"

description:
2️⃣ A blade that has taken on a much lighter form, and looks pretty slick now.
Imbued with "Liquid", may apply \State[10](10%) on-hit, designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: Rain Edge

description:
3️⃣⭐ Supposedly the embodiment of agility, and does indeed improve hit and parry chances.
Designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: "Agility"

description:
3️⃣ A blade that is too hot to touch! It seems forging with rouge has a heat-like elemental effect.
Imbued with "Heat", may apply \State[9](10%) on-hit, designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: Blaze Edge

description:
4️⃣⭐ Supposedly the embodiment of power, and does indeed improve critical and counter chances.
Designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: "Power"

description:
6️⃣⭐⭐ When forged in the fires of battle, the true force of a weapon is revealed.
Designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: "Force"

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ A masterfully refined upgrade to agility, this blade truly is swiftness incarnate.
Designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: "Swiftness"

description:
8️⃣ A ruthless blade powered by the flames of the finest Rouge.
Imbued with "Heat", may apply \State[9](20%) on-hit, designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: Vulcan Edge

description:
9️⃣ A gorgeous edge that is capable of a torrent of strikes in no time.
Imbued with "Liquid", may apply \State[10](20%) on-hit, designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: Torrent Edge

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended blade that drips with a lethal poison that will seal healing of any kind.
May apply \State[14](20%) on-hit, designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: "Hrunting"

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended blade that defines its own fate, having sharpness that defies critical RNG.
Designed to be dual-wielded with another weapon.
name: "Nægling"

description:
1️⃣ While it is technically a spear-class weapon, this is still just a fucking stick.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Pokey Stick

description:
2️⃣ Your standard-issue solder's iron spear.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Iron Spear

description:
3️⃣⭐ It might be... from a foreign land... but it also might be a knock-off... At least it looks flashy?
Wielded in both hands, may apply \State[15](25%) on-hit.
name: "Akai Supeeya"

description:
5️⃣ A large and beautiful halberd, the finest spear thing a medievel soldier could find.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Halberd

description:
6️⃣⭐⭐ The lethality of this blade is unmistakable. Blood everywhere.
Wielded in both hands, may apply \State[15](50%) on-hit.
name: "Crimson Stabber"

description:
7️⃣ Effectively a sword on a stick, and its effective at what it does.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Naginata

description:
9️⃣ Fancy for trident, but forged with the precision of Masamune.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Sankaku Yari

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended spear that is makes you bleed just by looking at it.
Wielded in both hands, applies \State[15] on-hit.
name: "Rhongomyniad"

description:
2️⃣ Though this is classified as a "spear", it is rather more a ball on a stick.
Wielded in both hands, may apply \State[8](5%) on-hit.
name: Basher

description:
4️⃣⭐ At this point, we aren't even trying to hide the lack of spear-ness.
Imbued with "Ground", may apply \State[12](25%) and \State[8](10%) on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: "Concussivity"

description:
5️⃣ We aren't getting any closer, but this absolutely will smash some skulls.
Wielded in both hands, may apply \State[8](5%) on-hit.
name: Smasher

description:
7️⃣ A flashy and fabulously smashtastic weapon for bashing your foes.
Wielded in both hands, may apply \State[8](5%) on-hit.
name: Flasher

description:
8️⃣⭐⭐ A massive hammer designed for crushing skulls- exactly as you aim to do.
Imbued with "Ground", may apply \State[12](50%) on-hit and \State[8](10%) on-hit, wielded in both hands.
name: "Ground Pounder"

description:
9️⃣ A deadly and dangerous "spear", far and beyond something to poke with, just shove it at them.
Wielded in both hands, may apply \State[8](5%) on-hit.
name: Clasher

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended smashing tool, crafted by a legendary smith of unparalleled skill.
Imbued with "Ground", applies \State[12] and maybe \State[8](15%) on-hit, wielded in both hands, destroys shielded foes.
name: "Daedalus"

description:
2️⃣ A light and thin spear designed for throwing.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Javelin

description:
4️⃣⭐ Excellent at piercing any type of aquatic animal thanks to its razor sharp point.
Wielded in both hands.
name: "Fish Eater"

description:
5️⃣ An excellent harpoon that was used in ancient times to puncture whale hide.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Whaling Harpoon

description:
6️⃣ While sharp spears are great, exploding spears are typically even greater.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Kaboom Needle

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ The addition of serration enables slaying both aquatic and reptiles effortlessly.
Wielded in both hands.
name: "Sauroter"

description:
9️⃣ Exacerbating explosive spears leads to super deadly and explosive spears.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Harisakeru

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended javelin said to pierce anything, including aquatics, reptiles, and deities.
Wielded in both hands.
name: "Vel"

description:
1️⃣ A rather old revolver that barely operates. By barely, we mean
it operates fully, but looks very ugly and is a tier-1 weapon.
name: Old Revolver

description:
2️⃣ A standard everyday pistol.
Shoots bullets, in case you were unaware.
name: Beretta

description:
4️⃣⭐ A pistol that fires angry bullets to slay its foes.
Imbued with "Heat", has high crit.
name: "Burning Bullet"

description:
5️⃣ A magnum, the king of classic pistols.
Fires with a over-compensating BANG💥.
name: Magnum

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ A raging pistol powered by your hatred.
Imbued with "Heat", has high crit.
name: "Hellfire Shot"

description:
8️⃣ If two magnums had a baby, it'd be this.
Because it blows you into chunks with a single shot.
name: Deagle

description:
9️⃣ Thanks to advancements in technology,
your gun now looks as cool as it is lethal.
name: KS Model 1337

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended pistol that basically breathes flame bullets on your behalf.
Imbued with "Heat", has high crit.
name: "Xiuhcoatl"

description:
2️⃣ A stun gun with a weak battery.
It is effectively a training weapon at this point.
name: 10-Volt Stun Gun

description:
3️⃣⭐ A bugzapper that had some DIY work to make it projectile-worthy.
Destroys insects.
name: "Fly Zapper"

description: 4️⃣ After replacing the battery, the stun gun is now a STUN GUN.
name: Butthole Tingler

description: 6️⃣ An extremely well-advertised and obviously good brand of battery powers this stun gun.
name: 10000-Volt Stun Gun

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ If you continue to overcharge a bugzapper, it'll start destroying foliage, too.
Destroys insects and plants.
name: "Defoliant"

description: 9️⃣ Packing a massive battery, you can release untold torrents of destruction on your foes.
name: Teravolt Shocker

description:
⭐⭐⭐ A stun gun with an ascended battery, capable of obliterating all of humanity.
Destroys insects, plants, and humanoids.
name: "Teen Baan"

description:
2️⃣ Your standard in shotguns. A bit heavy and rusty, but requires less effort.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Scattershot

description:
3️⃣⭐ A unique-shaped gun for blasting holes through bitches.
Destroys undead.
name: "Blaster"

description:
4️⃣ A triple-barrel shotgun for firing three times at once.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Tribarrel

description:
6️⃣ A 10-barrel shotgun for firing ten times at once.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Decabarrel

description:
8️⃣⭐⭐ A ruthless shotgun for dealing with your average zombie apocalypse.
Destroys undead.
name: "Spray of Death"

description:
9️⃣ A 100-barrel shotgun for firing ...not 100 times at once, but it does hit a lot!
Wielded in both hands.
name: Centibarrel

description:
⭐⭐⭐ A shotgun with ascended barrels for obliterating even beezlebub in one shot.
Banishes undead.
name: "Astra"

description: 1️⃣ A hatchet that is fairly rusty.
name: Rusty Hatchet

description:
2️⃣ A beginner's maul designed for easing woodchopping, but laced with a common diuretic.
May apply \State[16](25%).
name: Wolftrap Maul

description:
3️⃣⭐ A small glowing axe, which feels static to the touch.
Destroys constructs.
name: "Glowing Hacker"

description:
5️⃣ A heavy maul capable of doing some serious damage, laced with a mean poison.
May apply \State[16](50%).
name: Venomous Cleaver

description:
6️⃣⭐⭐ A dangerously charged and long axe that cleaves the skies.
Destroys constructs.
name: "Sky Splitter"

description:
7️⃣ A wicked axe with a tremendous heft to it, laced with a nasty poison.
May apply \State[16](75%).
name: Noxious Maul

description:
9️⃣ An axe glazed entirely with the most lethal venom in the galaxy: the Deathtrap.
Applies \State[16].
name: Deathtrap Maul

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended axe- I mean chainsaw- capable of rending all asunder.
Destroys constructs.
name: "Mjolnir"

description:
2️⃣ A rather large axe used by knights far and wide.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Knight's Axe

description:
4️⃣⭐ A beautiful crescent-shaped weapon for cleaving foes with ease.
Destroys humanoids, wielded in both hands.
name: "Crescent Blossom"

description:
5️⃣ A huge axe used by knights far and wide.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Angery Sagaris

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ A beautiful crescent-shaped weapon for cleaving foes with ease.
Destroys humanoids, wielded in both hands.
name: "Half-Moon Bloom"

description:
8️⃣ An ornamental axe from the days of the vikings of Earth.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Raging Battleaxe

description:
9️⃣ A massive axe wielded by a once-legendary berserker.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Berserker Labrys

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended scythe for when you are done with the the living.
Destroys humanoids, wielded in both hands.
name: "Ecliptic Efflorescence"

description:
2️⃣ Dual-ender weapons are trendy, but this one isn't very practical.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Twin Slasher

description:
3️⃣⭐ A fancy baton of sorts, fancily designed to deal with enemy weapons.
Destroys armed foes, wielded with both hands.
name: "Trainee Baton"

description:
4️⃣ A walking stick with blades on either end that are rather sharp.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Bladed Rungu

description:
6️⃣ Both offensive and defensive, this war weapon is capable of saving and taking lives.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Madu

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ The \Weapon[112] is enhanced to deal with both weapons and armor.
Destroys armed and shielded foes, wielded with both hands.
name: "Expert Jitsu"

description:
9️⃣ A dangerous and effective weapon with moonblades of death on either end.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Lajatang

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended dual-ender designed with the power of null.
Destroys humanoids, armed/shielded foes, wielded with both hands.
name: "Kaladanda"

description: 1️⃣ A plain (but probably slightly magical) wooden staff.
name: Aged Crook

description:
2️⃣ A well-made oaken staff, a proper accompaniment to any aspiring mage.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Oak Staff

description:
3️⃣⭐ A glowing ember, representing magical things.
Imbued with "Heat", may apply \State[9](25%), wielded in both hands.
name: "Flame's Mind"

description:
5️⃣ An oaken staff adorned with dreamcatcher-like mesh.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Mage Staff

description:
6️⃣⭐⭐ The will of the flame shaman howls silently inside this staff.
Imbued with "Heat", may apply \State[9](50%), wielded in both hands.
name: "Shaman's Will"

description:
7️⃣ Compressing the sheer magical energies of ages past result in potent magics today.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Ancient Crook

description:
9️⃣ An ancient relic of the shaman's of past. The kawaii ones, obviously.
Wielded in both hands.
name: Bedazzled Staff

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended staff embodying the carnal desires of the flame.
Wielded in both hands, applies \State[9],
name: "Ruyi"

description:
2️⃣ A cute wand bearing a couple of dangling kappa scales for extra magical oomph.
Deconstructs slimes.
name: Blue Wand

description:
3️⃣ An ornate rod adorned with sapphires to amplify its magical properties.
Deconstructs slimes.
name: Sapphire Rod

description:
4️⃣⭐ It looks like a large stalagmite, but it is translucent and radiating magical energies.
Imbued with "Liquid", may apply \State[10](25%) on-hit.
name: "Wet Dream"

description:
6️⃣⭐⭐ Further empowered with crystalline power, the depths are endless.
Imbued with "Liquid", may apply \State[10](50%) on-hit.
name: "Azure Depths"

description:
7️⃣ An extremely light wand designed to trace arcane sigils in the air.
Deconstructs slimes.
name: Tracing Wand

description:
9️⃣ Adorned with the power of the stars, this wand knows no bounds.
Deconstructs slimes.
name: Stardust Rod

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended rod of mythic proportions, said to control all liquid universally.
Imbued with "Liquid", applies \State[10] on-hit.
name: "Was"

description:
2️⃣ An aging tome with words barely legible.
Probably contains some degree of magic.
name: Old Tome

description:
3️⃣⭐ An old tome probably found in the restricted section of the library.
Imbued with "Void", may apply \State[14](25%).
name: "Tonguetwister"

description:
4️⃣ A book with binding made from all the furs of the monsters it has defeated.
Slays beasts.
name: Book of Beasts

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ An ancient tome full of diabolical secrets.
Imbued with "Void", may apply \State[14](50%).
name: "Secret Archive"

description:
8️⃣ A vast codex of unending knowledge about beasts and their deepest secrets.
Slays beasts.
name: Primal Codex

description:
9️⃣ The final works of one of the grandest archmages to ever live, \_ever\_.
Slays beasts.
name: Surreal Opus

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended tome with the ancient sigils describing how to control the gods.
Imbued with "Void", applies \State[14], defeats deities.
name: "Rauðskinna"

description:
1️⃣ A glove that has seen many an action.
What that action was remains a mystery, so just wear it.
name: Worn Glove

description: 2️⃣ You only punch with one hand, so just put them both on the same hand for extra power!
name: Leather Fists

description:
3️⃣⭐ The royal fists of an ancient probably important but not to you bloodline.
Obliterates shielded foes.
name: "Royal Fist"

description:
5️⃣ Mighty hands studded with rocks and shit.
Imbued with "Ground", smooshes bugs.
name: Studded Hands

description:
6️⃣⭐⭐ The might of the supreme reign true, enabling even crossdimensional foes to fall to your might.
Obliterates shielded and aurific foes.
name: "Supreme Metacarpus"

description:
7️⃣ Fists made of pure granite, meaning they are unbearably heavy.
Imbued with "Ground", smooshes bugs.
name: Granite Gloves

description:
9️⃣ Fists that radiate ground energy, possibly related to \N[3].
Imbued with "Ground", smooshes bugs.
name: Terra Fists

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended fist that can pummel even crossdimensional beings to dust.
Obliterates shielded foes, aural foes, and deities.
name: "Hecatoncheire"

description:
2️⃣ Sometimes it is more efficient to cut rather than beat things to death.
Ignores 10% of parry.
name: Metal Claws

description:
3️⃣⭐ A pair of soft mitts that are rather comfortable but with razor sharp blades.
Ignores 33% of parry.
name: "Bladed Mitts"

description:
4️⃣ Sometimes just beating them senseless doesn't work.
Ignores 20% of parry, slays beasts.
name: Cat Claws

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ Each of the 40 blades on this claw were precision-sharpened with a whetstone.
Ignores 66% of parry.
name: "Whetted Hands"

description:
8️⃣ Sharp claws like the talons of an eagle, your slashes can penetrate the most durable hides.
Ignores 30% of parry, annihilates flying foes.
name: Eagle Talons

description:
9️⃣ The literal claws of a dragon, ripped out and used to intimidate prey.
Ignores 40% of parry, decimates reptiles.
name: Dragon Claws

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended set of claws for tearing through reality like paper.
Cannot be parried.
name: "Death Knell"

description:
2️⃣ A light mechanical enhancement for your arm used to tear apart robots.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](5%).
name: Basic Arm

description:
3️⃣⭐ A cybernetic wonder, with some tutorials on kicking machine ass.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](15%).
name: "Meta Arm"

description:
4️⃣ A rather heavy but effective arm for knocking foes around.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](15%).
name: Heavy Arm

description:
5️⃣ Use this cruel arm enhancement to crush your foes without mercy or remorse.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](20%).
name: Cruel Support

description:
7️⃣⭐⭐ A mechanical masterpiece, constructed by Sybirtek™ for your combat pleasure.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](15%).
name: "Sybirtek Arm"

description:
9️⃣ A ruthless arm extension for demolishing constructs.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](40%).
name: Defense Buster

description:
⭐⭐⭐ An ascended mechano-arm programmed with self-healing knowledge and mechanical destruction.
Disassembles constructs, may apply \State[8](40%).
name: "Járngreipr"
